    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Very simple press <code>Clr + F</code> to open <strong>Find/Replace</strong> panel and check <strong>[✓] Regex</strong> copy past regex</p>\n\n<p><strong>Find:</strong> <code>[_]{1,1}([a-z])</code></p>\n\n<p><strong>Replace:</strong> <code>\\U$1</code></p>\n\n<p>Press [Replace all] button, Enjoy</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>Thanks @piotrek for <code>_some_awe_var</code> to <code>_someAweVar</code> </p>\n\n<p>Use Find: <code>(\\w)[_]{1,1}([a-z])</code> <br/>\nReplace: <code>$1\\U$2</code></p>\n"
  }, {
