    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>If you are OK with PyCharm also refactoring usages, launch the \"Rename\" tool (Refactor > Rename). The window pops up with drop down list and you should see the snake_case version of the text in the list (you can open the window and switch to the snake_case with key-strokes so it can be pretty fast).</p>\n"
