      "body" : "For your CamelCase to snake_case, you better make sure you have something selected.  As written it will replace every single capital letter in your project to a lowercase proceeded by an underscore.  That seems bad to me.  At very least you need to limit it to something like <code>(?&lt;=[a-z])([A-Z])</code> to get only capitals that follow a lowercase."
