    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<h2>From snake_case to CamelCase</h2>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Find: <code>(\\w)[_]{1,1}([a-z])</code></li>\n<li>Replace: <code>$1\\U$2</code></li>\n<li>Settings: \n\n<ul>\n<li>Match Case</li>\n<li>Regex</li>\n</ul></li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2>From CamelCase to snake_case:</h2>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Find: <code>([A-Z])</code></li>\n<li>Replace: <code>\\_\\L$1</code></li>\n<li>Settings: \n\n<ul>\n<li>Match Case</li>\n<li>Regex</li>\n</ul></li>\n</ul>\n"
  } ],
